{"tid":2188677,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［活蛇金主］巴塞主席被控在抺黑功臣事件中存在貪污之嫌","createTime":"2020-09-04T11:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T01:30:03.000Z","uid":90515,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f76ace1030cbe911aa785184b1c5578438885a","tid":2188677,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"根據西班牙第二大報章《El Mundo》報導，球會主席巴杜美奧被加泰隆尼亞警方控以瀆職罪名。加泰警方在針對巴杜美奧的調查及指控後得出結論，確認他在今年的「公關門事件」醜聞中存有貪污的證據。<br />\n<br />\n據稱他涉嫌以球會開支僱用公關公司，大肆抹黑以美斯、沙維丶碧基丶佩奧爾等人為首的「反巴杜美奧派」球員和名宿。報道指，該筆款項由巴杜美奧親自批核，而且更高於該公關公司平常收費的整整六倍。因此他有以權謀私及貪污之嫌，被加泰警方介入調查。"},{"pid":"b7d51e0d9aa4b1e182a8478980e6b75b22a93970","tid":2188677,"uid":90515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:29:18.000Z","msg":"唔怪得活蛇咁努力出po，原來收成六倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28d4c60f95a6cc7ad0ad9c4be85bd2d0a93aad0","tid":2188677,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"咪屈啦<br />\n活蛇係新浪同虎撲打手啫"},{"pid":"0750c3006ef608a0425f3b1e7fbf3e1d27913e6c","tid":2188677,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a28d4c60f95a6cc7ad0ad9c4be85bd2d0a93aad0","tid":2188677,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"咪屈啦<br />\n活蛇係新浪同虎撲打手啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"活蛇好球！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99f3bbe4cbb368555783bd6fbcb996ed43feae4","tid":2188677,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"活蛇金主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c740e69023da00669ff25a57012e0b6bb755e235","tid":2188677,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7d51e0d9aa4b1e182a8478980e6b75b22